{"tid":669443,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"VR GAME發展咁慢,而家出左等於冇出","createTime":"2018-05-18T12:28:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T07:20:20.000Z","uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d0bf4497b4486eed5ed973b1ca6047bd54ab8720","tid":669443,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-18T12:28:10.000Z","msg":"幾乎冇人理<br />\n好多人己經封塵"},{"pid":"1b87ec9fd05e56a2b89d15bd28f1d3cb1d4abfe1","tid":669443,"uid":33939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T04:51:01.000Z","msg":"wii, kinect vr....<br />\n吹到大一大，係有班友信真係前途無限，依家呢？"},{"pid":"edb1c52247db5e35bc7d92d49e0c942062430ffd","tid":669443,"uid":82743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:00:24.000Z","msg":"除左RE7之外真係無game係又正又VR"},{"pid":"06b7e4d89b54051afd335af5b2af90ef70d63c6b","tid":669443,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:08:29.000Z","msg":"成本貴  你認為vr真係好易整？<br />\n換來係你都唔識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cf76207bb2c37d1fec5c007681d80a13905ee4","tid":669443,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"畫質咁差，不了"},{"pid":"5f30a1adeb2736aa2ca283faf05173912bcc1b8f","tid":669443,"uid":38550,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:24:41.000Z","msg":"vr 唔應該target 打機撚的<br />\n尤其是啲鎗game 運動game<br />\n大部分打機撚都係咁唔想郁或者綜合體力唔夠先對住個mon 唔落場<br />\n<br />\n應該調返轉target 玩war game 玩運動嘅人<br />\n用vr 幫手增加樂趣<br />\n或者vr 配合飛機杯<br />\n呢啲先有前景"},{"pid":"63cc2df53d4d2db3621c04a210ffd4d32b8fdbf8","tid":669443,"uid":59608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:33:18.000Z","msg":"try vrchat"},{"pid":"5551a64ace44d745c8d5e0813b66abeef5b40b8c","tid":669443,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:38:21.000Z","msg":"Vr av"},{"pid":"2a335e7128a71864a8b65e19de7d791527389050","tid":669443,"uid":80323,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:40:30.000Z","msg":"少人有VR設備，game廠自然唔肯出VR game<br />\n<br />\n而加真係出VR 3A大作既話，要htc vive/oculus rift+高階/頂級PC先玩到，可能仲要有一D動作輸入設備(例如渣車要軚盤)，咁既設備得好少玩家有。出隻高技術VR game，銷量一定好低，會蝕錢/無錢賺，遊戲公司點會肯出。<br />\n<br />\n不過VR設備普及之後，VR game應該會發展得唔錯。問題係可能好多年之後先普及到有VR 3A大作，因為而加遊戲公司下下都會遷就家用機出game。家用機現時既趨勢係用垃圾CPU，分分鐘到PS7先run到VR 3A大作。"},{"pid":"73d3fdd3e47dad3852fb6ff95881e79ccbf6c180","tid":669443,"uid":116519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:44:55.000Z","msg":"咁多vr game得隻beat saber我覺得好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申:無玩過vr"},{"pid":"a49f6251e4d38a55a992e8f8c5fd0bacbf62381f","tid":669443,"uid":74970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:58:03.000Z","msg":"未出已經唔睇好VR, 除左玩H GAME, 睇AV之外<br />\n打機就算9數啦, 初初就有新鮮感, 後尾你都懶得用啦<br />\n就算出到大作都無用, 第一人稱限制太多, 來來去去都只會係果堆games<br />\n唔會有咩突破, 吹到vr會對遊戲有革命性改變真係得啖笑"},{"pid":"347b99e673d1295f9edc84cadf6c0f5d4a9c3f77","tid":669443,"uid":73054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T05:59:29.000Z","msg":"最大問題係硬件追唔上"},{"pid":"f9eeb0c4510f4799f4edfd4e0c3dbb20d268424b","tid":669443,"uid":130568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T07:20:20.000Z","msg":"中國首個VR 樂園於貴陽開幕斥資37 億興建<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/05/16/chinese-first-vr-park/life-tech/travel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F05%2F16%2Fchinese-first-vr-park%2Flife-tech%2Ftravel%2F&d=V6JraWaE4za4%2B6keL3aCfJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=745ad7e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/05/16/chinese-first-vr-park/life-tech/travel/</a><br />\n<br />\n直擊 VR ZONE Shinjuku 日本最大 VR 機舖試玩 !<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/07/14/vrzone/japan-gadget/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F07%2F14%2Fvrzone%2Fjapan-gadget%2F&d=V6JraWaE4za4%2B6keL3aCfJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f5f35268\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/07/14/vrzone/japan-gadget/</a><br />\n<br />\nVR有一個好大既問題就係暈，視覺同身體移動唔同步<br />\n所以發展放咗響體驗市場<br />\n<br />\n家用VR起碼要2K、120FPS先叫成熟<br />\n但成本太高，做唔到普級化"}]}